WEBVTT

00:10:59.735 --> 00:11:01.417
To put that in perspective,

00:11:01.417 --> 00:11:03.090
a 23 percent increase

00:11:03.090 --> 00:11:06.975
is like trading in your
1980 Chevy Citation

00:11:06.975 --> 00:11:11.619
for a 1980 Chevrolet Corvette.

00:11:11.619 --> 00:11:14.131
We were so excited by this,

00:11:14.131 --> 00:11:16.298
because this meant that a strategy

00:11:16.298 --> 00:11:17.980
that costs nothing,

00:11:17.980 --> 00:11:19.747
that is easy for people to use,

00:11:19.747 --> 00:11:21.718
regardless of whether they're in shape

00:11:21.718 --> 00:11:23.576
or struggling to get there,

00:11:23.576 --> 00:11:25.016
had a big effect.

00:11:25.016 --> 00:11:26.573
Keeping your eyes on the prize

00:11:26.573 --> 00:11:29.517
made the exercise look and feel easier

00:11:29.517 --> 00:11:32.075
even when people were working harder